title: Tybee Island Recap; Carl Nassib Comes Out
itunes:title: Tybee Island Recap; Carl Nassib Comes Out
description:
A room full of some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Ricky Hollywood recap their amazing trip to Tybee Island, Georgia to celebrate the life of Chris Wesseling. Raiders DE Carl Nassib comes out as gay becoming the first active NFL player to do so. Also, Eli Manning is BACK with the Giants (52:50).
